        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 85. Hind tibia lectotype adult male S. minor showing 3 inner (left photo) and 1 outer (right photo) spines. He is missing his right rear leg. Given that the allotype female from the same locality has 3 outer tibial spines, we suspect that the lectotype male suffered some damage to his left tibia when an earlier instar." ;
